<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.10">
<l>tiṅkaḷtōy māṭa nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉai</l>
<l>maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ vaṇtārk kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ vallār</l>
<l>poṅkunī rulaka māṇṭu poṉṉula kāṇṭu piṉṉum</l>
<l>veṅkatirp pariti vaṭṭat tūṭupōy viḷaṅku vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the poems of Kaliyaṉ with a fresh garland,</l>
<l rend="indent">leader of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>About the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where mansions touch the moon,</l>
<l>Having ruled the world with roiling seas, having ruled the golden world,</l>
<l>Then having gone through the corona of the hot-rayed disc,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will be effulgent.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
